}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About/FAQ Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: navy;
            font-size: 18px;
            background-color: #b0c4de;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background-color: white;
        }

        h1 {
            color: navy;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 32px;
        }

        h3 {
            color: navy;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            .button:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
            }

        .contact-form {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .contact-form.show {
                display: block;
            }

        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

            .input-group label {
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .input-group textarea {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 8px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
            }

        .message {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #155724;
            display: none;
      


        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>


    <div class="container">
        <h1>About</h1>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>What this website is about</h3>
            <p>This website allows users to rate how bad their Asthma was in a certain city, relative to the weather conditions of that day.</p>
            <p>Users are able to browse and see ratings for their desired city!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>How to use the Webstie</h3>
            <p>Below is a step by step guide to using the website:</p>
            <ol>
            <li>
                First you must select your desired City for which you woulud like to see reviews. Alternatively, you may Browse By City, which allows you to customize your sort.
            </li>
            <li>
                Then, you select whether you would like to see the reviews for today for that City, or look at past reviews.
            </li>
            <li>
                After making your selection, you may browse other reviews!
            </li>
            <li>To make a review, on the main menu type in your desired City, then hit make a review.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>FAQ</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Why isn't my location showing up?<br>Our website only looks at cities within the United States. If your city is not available, you may submit a request for us to add it below.</li>
                <li>What do you do with my data? <br /> Absolutely nothing! The purpose of the user is to make and see reviews, nothing more.</li>
                <li>How can I make a donation?<br />We currently are not accepting donations, but we thank you!</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <a href="#" class="btn bg-warning text-white" id="contactButton">Request City</a>

        <div class="contact-form" id="contactForm">
            <form action="#" method="post" id="contactForm">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="message">City Request:</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <button type="submit" id="submitButton" class="btn btn-primary">Send</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="message" id="messageSent">City Requested!</div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-left: auto;">
        <a href="AMain" class="btn bg-warning text-white">Return</a>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById("contactButton").addEventListener("click", function (event) {
            event.preventDefault();
            document.getElementById("contactForm").classList.toggle("show");
            document.getElementById("messageSent").style.display = "none";
        });

        document.getElementById("submitButton").addEventListener("click", function (event) {
            event.preventDefault();
            document.getElementById("messageSent").style.display = "block";
            document.getElementById("contactForm").reset();
            setTimeout(function () {
                document.getElementById("messageSent").style.display = "none";
            }, 3000);
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>
